title: Literatura Internacional: A CHILD'S HISTORY OF ENGLAND
info: SinopseCharles Dickens - A Childs History of England is a book by Charles Dickens. It first appeared in serial form in Household Words, running from January 25, 1851 to December 10, 1853. Dickens also published the work in book form in three volumes: the first volume on December 20, 1851; the second, December 25, 1852; and the third, December 24, 1853. Although the volumes were published in December, each was postdated the following year.
